Mereka membawa beberapa jujube.

544
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:15,840
Cobalah, manis atau tidak.

545
00:37:16,120 --> 00:37:17,399
Pastinya manis.

546
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:19,919
Kau masih belum coba.

547
00:37:20,199 --> 00:37:21,800
Kenapa tahu pasti manis?

548
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:22,479
Aku...

549
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:25,679
