557
00:38:02,600 --> 00:38:05,280
Ternyata istana dipenuhi pelangi.

558
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:08,159
Sayangnya dulu tak
pernah memperhatikan.

559
00:38:08,560 --> 00:38:10,159
Hanya tahu melihat ke langit.

560
00:38:12,560 --> 00:38:14,639
Terima kasih, Tuan Fang.

561
